Needs to be root to run.

$ sudo million-quid-drop/quiz.py


Loosely based on the pygame example in the O'Reilly "Python, PyGame, and Raspberry Pi Game Development" book
by Sloan Kelly - chaper 23.

Some useful reference URLs below:

https://learning.oreilly.com/library/view/python-pygame-and/9781484245330/html/435550_2_En_23_Chapter.xhtml
https://gpiozero.readthedocs.io/en/stable/index.html
https://www.pygame.org/docs/

https://www.reddit.com/r/raspberry_pi/comments/erudaa/gpio_in_my_pygame_python_script/

https://mixkit.co/free-sound-effects/game/

